	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />When I couldn't get some macro stuff to work with WLA today I got
<br />pretty annoyed and thought about what else I could try. I ended up
<br />compiling binutils (2.16) for 65816. Later versions dropped
<br />support completely, but &lt;=2.16 will do.
<br />
<br />The real problem is writing a linker script for the ld though. Not
<br />only is the syntax rather cryptic, it's also probably not really 
<br />intended to be used with a layout like on the snes, i.e rom banking.
<br />
<br />Should anyone here have experience with this though, feel free
<br />to give me some hints... :)

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


